### Analytics Service API Tests
### Port: 3007
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3007

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get period metrics for a company - Monthly
### Replace {companyId} with actual UUID
@companyId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics/company/{{companyId}}/period/2024-01
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get period metrics for a company - Quarterly
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics/company/{{companyId}}/period/2024-Q1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get SROI report for a company
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics/sroi/{{companyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get SROI report with date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics/sroi/{{companyId}}?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get VIS report for a company
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics/vis/{{companyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get VIS report with date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics/vis/{{companyId}}?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Trigger aggregation for all companies
POST {{baseUrl}}/metrics/aggregate
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Trigger aggregation for specific company
POST {{baseUrl}}/metrics/aggregate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}"
}

###

### Trigger aggregation for specific period
POST {{baseUrl}}/metrics/aggregate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "period": "2024-01"
}

###
